    "content": "Dassault Falcon 900B LED Cabin Lighting from PWI, Inc. Home / Aircraft Lighting / Falcon 900B LED Cabin Lighting Systems Approved LED Aircraft Lighting Falcon 900B LED Cabin Lighting Systems Part Numbers 6910100-000 and 6910100-007 PMA PQ4159CE Supplement 23 LEDs Replace Cabin Fluorescents Long Life, No Maintenance Solution 3-Year Warranty Designed and Manufactured in the USA Approved Aircraft Dassault Falcon 900B Overview PWI, Inc., the original cabin lighting supplier for the Dassault Falcon 900B, has a replacement LED cabin lighting system. This PMA-approved system replaces all PWI fluorescent lights in the passenger cabin with modern LEDs. The Cool White 5100K color temperature LEDs are delivered with aircraft-matching electrical connectors. No aircraft modifications required. Refresh the cabin of your Falcon 900B with new LEDs from PWI, Inc. Email for Pricing Download Product Information 8 photos Benefits 100,000-hour service life. Direct replacement for original fluorescents in main cabin, lav, and galley. LEDs take the place of each fluorescent. Reuse the original aircraft electrical wiring. Very low power draw and low heat. No maintenance required. Installation Uses original aircraft wiring and original dimming controls. No soldering or aircraft modifications required. Two LED systems available - one for each 900B cabin lighting layout. Product Details System Specs Part Numbers 6910100-000 / 6910100-007 Operating Life (minimum) 100,000 Hours Input Voltage 28V from aircraft Color Temperature 5100K cool white Number of Lights 40 or 64 (configuration-dependent) Installation Direct Replacement Connectors Aircraft-matching electrical connectors included Key Benefits 100,000-hour operation Operates on 28V aircraft power Solid-state LED technology Eliminates fluorescent flicker and ballast noise No more cold weather slow starts Eliminates ongoing maintenance Uses original aircraft electrical wiring Part Numbers & Serial Number Compatibility One system for each of two Falcon 900B cabin layouts. Aircraft serial number needed to provide a quote. Aircraft Model Configuration Number of Lights Falcon 900B Louvered headliner and downwash lights 64 Falcon 900B Upwash and downwash lights 40 Also Available Compatible LED Reading Lights 303 LED 28V Lamp 1308 / 1309 LED 28V Lamp 1495 LED 28V Lamp"
