    "content": "Contact & Quote — PGISR by PWI Home / Contact Get in touch Let's talk about your property. Tell us what you're protecting and when you need it. Our engineers will get back to you with a configuration recommendation and pricing — usually within 1–2 business days. Direct Contact Email sales@pwi-e.com Phone +1 316 942 2811 Fax +1 316 942 6209 Address 109 South Knight Street Wichita, Kansas 67213 USA Lead Time Standard lead time for configured sensor packages is 90–120 days from order confirmation. Contact us to discuss expedited options for urgent deployments. Part Number 1234567-999 Quote Request Form First Name * Last Name * Work Email * Organization Phone Application / Use Case Select a property type… Corporate Campus Private Estate / Residential Office Building Warehouse / Logistics Facility Industrial Site / Manufacturing Data Center Energy / Utilities Infrastructure Retail / Commercial Property Healthcare / Hospital Campus Other Sensors of Interest Select sensor type(s)… Magnetometer (Short Range) Magnetometer (Long Range) Radar Gas Detection FLIR (Thermal) Seismic Radioactivity Acoustic Camera (Pan/Tilt/Zoom) Multiple / Custom Configuration Property Details / Requirements Submit Quote Request By submitting this form you agree to be contacted by PWI, Inc. regarding your inquiry. View our Privacy Statement ."
